# Movie Rating Prediction with Python

CodSoft Data Science Internship - Task 2

## Objective
Build a machine learning model to predict movie ratings based on features such as genre, director, and actors.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Dataset
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/adrianmcmahon/imdb-india-movies

## Model
Linear Regression

## Features Used
- Genre
- Director
- Actors

